Can you help find Brian, 40, from Coatbridge, who was last seen on Monday?CONCERN is growing for a man who has gone missing from the Coatbridge area.Brian McTaggart, 40, was last seen on Monday.He is described as 5ft 8in tall, of heavy build, and is bald with blue eyes.When last seen, he was wearing jeans, a burgundy hooded top and white trainers.Anyone who has seen Brian, or knows of his whereabouts, is asked to contact Coatbridge Police on 101.